        {
            "title": "輕鐵內吸食太空油少女年僅13歲 $250街頭買太空油 初嘗毒品被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/12063fa119ecb782e041848acfc8308f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250307/_2025030716410641656.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近年青少年吸食新興毒品太空油有上升趨勢，有網民昨日（6日）拍攝到天水圍一名少女在輕鐵內懷疑吸食太空油毒品，神情呆滯腳步浮浮落車，之後更失平衡跌倒在輕鐵站月台上。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息指，該名少女年僅13歲，為一名中二學生，事發時間為昨日（6日）晚上7時左右。警方接獲市民報案，指在天水圍輕鐵車廂內及天瑞站月台附近，發現一名少女疑似吸食過毒品，人員其後在天瑞商場發現少女，並在她身上發現一支電子煙和一個懷疑太空油煙彈，隨即以涉嫌「藏有危險藥物」將她拘捕。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3435498/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E5%85%A7%E5%90%B8%E9%A3%9F%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%B2%B9%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81-%E8%85%B3%E6%AD%A5%E6%B5%AE%E6%B5%AE%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E6%B7%AA%E4%BA%A1\">網傳天水圍少女輕鐵內吸食太空油毒品 腳步浮浮落車 網民：真係道德淪亡</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>據了解，少女報稱前一日在街頭向一名陌生男子以250元購入煙彈，以往沒有吸毒的習慣，今次是首次嘗試太空油毒品，案件由天水圍警區軍裝巡邏第一小隊跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124313/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"前方的女學生察覺有異樣，向後張望。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62c41ad7f155682c486a1a4cb806e8d4/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_00_000.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        前方的女學生察覺有異樣，向後張望。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124312/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名穿杏色衫的少女坐在輕鐵列車的單人位，不斷拿著疑似電子煙煙機狂吸，吞雲吐霧。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a76a414e7a5056205b902e2c69ceaa6e/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_01_229.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名穿杏色衫的少女坐在輕鐵列車的單人位，不斷拿著疑似電子煙煙機狂吸，吞雲吐霧。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124311/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"前方的女學生察覺有異樣，立即離開座位。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e099a09c572262adfac168d0640f90e/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_04_590.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        前方的女學生察覺有異樣，立即離開座位。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124310/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"少女未有理會車廂其他人的目光，繼續吸食。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/faf40ae7e1666fdf8efd887a6dbc2104/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_11_476.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        少女未有理會車廂其他人的目光，繼續吸食。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124309/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"少女緩緩站起身，神情呆滯腳步浮浮落車。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/605a97ae9cfd3ef2118fba5ef32ae4c1/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_12_463.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        少女緩緩站起身，神情呆滯腳步浮浮落車。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124308/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"少女緩緩站起身，神情呆滯腳步浮浮落車。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c3d41b14aeae12429f222de7e9b44c8/2025-03/AQOeEgFTDILDp_H9FqOvoKCDW0SdPQT69x_yb91lhsS1qfiu77_a5wECaO3h3I5gU_5iNrKzFmyJ6a4qeg3HRohy_mp4_snapshot_00_15_574.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        少女緩緩站起身，神情呆滯腳步浮浮落車。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article clas